column3:
Hello, <Username>
Two types of body transformation "images" are provided to you and stored

Once at setup
This is your complete target weight - automatically saved that you processed on the previous screen

Weekly Image Change
Smaller weekly transformation images are provided to encourage you to complete your program
You will receive a push notification to capture your new image once a week - push notifications can be changed in your device settings

Daily Goal Journal
Input a few daily health stats in your goal journal each day

Awareness is Key
You will receive push notifications to input your daily calorie intake and exercise - this includes an optional rest day - you will receive award badges and trophies once you complete milestones - Once a week you process your new image & daily you will input calories and exercise, including optional rest day

The ACSM & CDC recommend, for good health, adults get at least 30 min of moderate aerobic activity five days per week or more - If activity is vigorous, the suggestion is 20 min sessions three or more days per week - Furthermore, it is recommended engaging in strength training a minimum of twice weekly
